[normal]10.3 LCC
[normal], advised by a transport expert and ex lorry driver, lobbied 
[normal]s
[normal]uccessfully 
[normal]for 
[normal]the inclusion in 
[normal]TfL
[normal] [bold]contracts of a requ
[normal]irement for lorry operators to:
[normal]&#xa0;
